{"tid":2451860,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃世柒：連登咁多五毛一定係習近平想發動文革！","createTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T18:49:12.000Z","uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3913d091a050445f1191c1a35167a03e6695a78b","tid":2451860,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係話習近平唔想發動文革，而係呢個論據太On9<br />\n<br />\n批評黃世柒=五毛=習近平想發動文革<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Za10w6Oyffk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZa10w6Oyffk&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=b29b106f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Za10w6Oyffk</a>"},{"pid":"0acd1b7bf5ee85ae58e7c0f54e33e33769b9a0ec","tid":2451860,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"2009年事跡<br />\n居歐權夢碎<br />\n黃世澤一直聲稱歐盟《里斯本條約》生效後，BNO持有人可以成為歐盟公民獲得居歐權，並言之鑿鑿已有BNO持有人成功闖關。<span class=\"red\"><strong>不少網民信以為真，並胡亂批評質疑的人為五毛黨</strong></span>，甚至聲言向平機會投訴高登。2009年12月1日，《里斯本條約》生效，謠言流傳達到顛峰，甚至有網民自稱已買了機票準備移民歐洲。"},{"pid":"9d29e443fb3f5bc15bae94a112f1d54cd8754d18","tid":2451860,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"批評佢=5毛，早係2011年已經有人提出<br />\n<br />\n黃世澤經常就網絡現象發表文章，在文字亦常流露對中共的厭惡，指她經常煽動「自己人打自己人」。<span class=\"red\"><strong>又認為網絡上充斥著大量五毛黨，對於與他意見或政見有別的網民留言黃皆認為是「五毛黨所為」</strong></span>，亦視他們的留言為「纏擾行為」，更多次表明擬以法律手段控告與他意見有別的網友 ，黃亦言明禁止網民將其博客文章轉載至討論區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%93%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25AD%2594%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2fZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=6d825e73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25AD%2594%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF&h=d0fbd07b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%93%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E9%AD%94%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF</a>"},{"pid":"14f0f7cd5986ccd8d1f57b7d6a7ce59a387bd1d9","tid":2451860,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"點解冇世柒話羅37識打機所以會入美軍既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6930f9e3bf3026f7d8d3e2d1d68c62d9f1fc62e","tid":2451860,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T21:51:17.000Z","msg":"原來信牙世澤9up的人係唔睇新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xJZzoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xJZzoS.png&h=629d691d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n鬼唔知習近平想發動文革<br />\n<ins>但牙世澤 link去屌自己的人就係習派完全係不知所謂</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友比人屌係因比25鎊扮英國政要呃人,<strong>講唔過人就屈人收共產黨錢仲鼓動其畜牲支持者亂咬人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">你玩邪教水到班支持者飲山澗水, 食碘片防核爆本來唔關我事<br />\n你點班匡智支持者糾纏我就係關我事</span>"},{"pid":"f39dff2e3dfa8ef737eb8a637faad43f9a4e493e","tid":2451860,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T18:49:12.000Z","msg":"世柒幾時去整返排牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}